.0500pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#9312;　</span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >NameNode:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >NameNode可以被认为是系统的主站。它维护所有系统中存在的文件和目</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:42.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:4.0000gd;text-indent:0.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >录的文件系统树和元数据。两个文件：</font>&#8220;命名空间映像&#8221;和&#8220;编辑日志&#8221;是用来存储元数据信息。Namenode有所有包含数据块为一个给定的文件中的数据节点的知识，但不存储块的位置持续。从数据节点在系统每次启动时信息重构一次。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:18.0500pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#9313;　</span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >DateNode:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >DataNodes作为从机，每台机器位于一个集群中，并提供实际的存储。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="mso-para-margin-left:2.0000gd;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >它负责为客户读写请求服务。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >HDFS中的读/写操作运行在块级。HDFS数据文件被分成块大小的块，这是作为独立的单元存储。默认块大小为64MB。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >HDFS操作是数据复制的概念，其中在数据块的多个副本被创建，分布在整个节点的集群以使在节点故障的情况下数据的高可用性。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >注：在</font>HDFS的文件中，比单个块小，不占用块的全部存储。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h2 style="mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.3<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >在</font>HDFS&nbsp;读操作：</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h2><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >数据读取请求将由</font>HDFS，NameNode和DataNode来服务。下图中Client为读取器。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >图片为读取</font>HDFS文件的流程。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span><img width="641"  height="453"  src="../assets/img/comproblemFour/img1719.png" ></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >客户端启动通过调用文件系统对象的</font>open（）方法读取请求。它是DistributedFileSystem类型的对象。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >此对象使用</font>RPC联接到namenode并获取的元数据信息如该文件的块的位置。注：这些地址是文件的前几个块。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >响应该元数据请求，具有该块副本的</font>DataNodes地址被返回。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦接收到</font>DataNodes的地址，FSDataInputSystem类型的一个对象被返回到客户端。FSDataInputSystem包含DFSInputStream这需要处理交互DataNode和NameNode。在上图所示的步骤4，客户端调用read（）方法，这将导致DFSInputStream建立与第一个DataNode文件的第一个块联接。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >以数据流的形式读取数据，其中客户端多次调用</font>&#8220;read（）&#8221;方法。read（）操作这个过程一直持续，知道它到达块结束的位置。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦到模块的结尾，</font>DFSInputStream关闭连接，移动定位到下一个DataNode的下一个块。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦客户端已读取完成后，它会调用</font>close（）方法。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h2 style="mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.4<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >在</font>HDFS&nbsp;写操作</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h2><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >流程图：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span><img width="642"  height="480"  src="../assets/img/comproblemFour/img2308.png" ></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >客户端通过调用</font>DistributeFileSystem对象的create（）方法创建一个新的文件，并开始写操作。&nbsp;（步骤1）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >DisttributedFileSystem对象使用RPC调用连接到NameNode，并启动新的文件创建。但是，此文件创建不与文件任何块相关联。NameNode的责任是验证文件（其正被创建）不存在，并且客户端具有正确权限来创建新文件。如果文件已经存在，或者客户端不具有足够的权限来创建一个新的文件，则抛出IOException到客户端。否则操作成功，并且该文件新的记录是由NameNode创建。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦</font>NameNode创建一条新的记录，返回FSDataOutputStream类型的一个对象到客户端。客户端使用它来写入数据到HDFS。数据写入方法被调用（步骤3）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >FSDataOutputStream包含DFSOutputStream对象，它使用DataNodes和NameNode通信后查找。当客户机继续写入数据，DFSOutputStream继续创建这个数据包。这些数据包联接排列到一个被称为DataQueue的队列。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >还有一个名为</font>DataStreamer组件，用于消耗DataQueue。DataStreamer也被要求NameNode分配新的块，拣选DataNodes用于复制。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >现在，复制过程始于使用</font>DataNodes创建一个管道。在图片中，选择了复制水平3，因此有3个DataNodes管道。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >所述</font>DataStreamer注入包分成到第一个DataNode的管道中。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >在每个</font>DataNode的管道中存储数据包接收并同样转发在第二个DataNode的管道中。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >另一个队列，</font>&#8220;Ack&nbsp;Queue&#8221;是由DFSOutputStream保持存储。它们是DataNodes等待确认的数据包。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦确认在队列中的分组从所有</font>DataNodes已接收在管道，它从&#8220;Ack&nbsp;Queue&#8221;删除。在任何DataNode发生故障时，从队列中的包重新用于操作。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >在客户端的数据写入完成后，它会调用</font>close（）方法,调用close（）结果进入到清理缓存剩余数据包到官道之后等待确认。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >一旦收到最终确认，</font>NameNode连接告诉它该文件的写操作完成。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >Hadoop-master&nbsp;中&nbsp;core-site.xml文件的配置</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><img width="424"  height="389"  src="../assets/img/comproblemFour/img3279.png" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><a name="OLE_LINK1" ></a><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >hdfs-site.xml文件</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h1 style="mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >三、</span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Oozie框架</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h1><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >参考网址：</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/data/library/bd-hadoopoozie/</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Oozie是用于Hadoop平台的工作流引擎。工作流定义通过将多个Hadoop&nbsp;job的定义按照一定的顺序组织起来，然后作为一个整体按照既定的路径运行。一个工作流已经定义了，通过启动该工作流job，就会执行该工作流中包含的多个Hadoop&nbsp;job，知道完成，这就是工作流job的生命周期。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >那么，现在我们有一个工作流</font>job，希望每天半夜00:00启动运行，我们能够想到的就是通过写一个定时脚本来调度程序运行。如果我们有多个工作流job，使用crontab的方式调用可能需要编写大量的脚本，还要通过脚本来控制好各个工作流job的执行时序问题。&nbsp;不但脚本不好维护，而且监控也不方便。基于这样的背景，Oozie提出了Coordinator的概念，他们能够将每个工作流job作为一个动作（Action）来运行，相当于工作流定义中的一个执行节点（我们可以理解为工作流的工作流），这样就能够将多个工作流Job组织起来。称为Coordinator&nbsp;job,并指定触发时间和频率，还可以配置数据集、并发数等。一个Coordinator&nbsp;job&nbsp;包含了在job外部设置执行周期和频率的语义，类似于在工作流外部增加了一个协调器来管理这些工作流job的运行。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EasyML使用Oozie框架来支持工作流，当通过前端页面设定好具体的工作流程后，会自动生成对应的XML文件&#8212;&#8212;workflow.xml</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h2 style="mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.5<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >工作流控制节点</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h2><h3 style="mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.5.1<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >启动控制节点。</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h3><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >是工作流作业的入口点。在工作流启动时，它会自动过渡到启动过程中的节点。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="border-top:1.0000pt solid windowtext;mso-border-top-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-right:1.0000pt solid windowtext;mso-border-right-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0000pt solid windowtext;mso-border-bottom-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0000pt solid w