o-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" >&nbsp;</span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >特征提取</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h3><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.9.1<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >词频</font>-逆向文件频率（TF-IDF）</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >TF-IDF是一种在文本挖掘中用来特征向量化的方法。统计出每个词语在语料库中的权重。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.9.2<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >Word2Vec</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >采用一系列文本数据来训练一个</font>word2vecmodel。将每个词语映射到一个固定大小的向量。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i>&nbsp;</i></span></p><h3 style="mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >特征变换</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h3><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.1<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >分词器</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >将文本数据中的句子分割成一个个词语。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.2<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >停用词移除</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >停用词：在文本中频繁出现，但是并没有承载太多意义的词语。对于算法来说没有任何意义。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.3<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >二值化</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >根据阈值将连续型的数值特征转换为</font>0--1特征的过程。&nbsp;在图片处理时经常使用二值化来将像素设为0-255，使得整个图片呈现出明显的黑和白的视觉效果。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.4<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >主成分分析（</font>PCA）</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;<font face="仿宋" >主成分分析是一种统计学方法，使用正交转换从一系列可能相关的变量中提取线性无关变</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >量集，提取出的变量集中的元素称为主成分。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.5<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >多项式展开</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:9.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >多项式展开通过产生</font>n维组合将原始特征拓展到多项式空间。例如对于（x,y）向量来说,如果我们以2维来进行展开的话，则转化为(x,x*x,y,x*y,y*y)向量。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h4 style="mso-list:l0 level4 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.7.10.6<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="仿宋" >离散余弦变换（</font>DCT）</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:仿宋;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h4><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span styl