nt:0.0000;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >2)<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><font face="宋体" >可在平台上共享数据、程序、任务流程和分析结果；</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=18  style="margin-left:21.2500pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.2500pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >3)<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><font face="宋体" >在一个任务中无缝整合单机算法和分布式算法，用户可在一个任务中同时包含</font>M/R,&nbsp;Spark,&nbsp;单机等多种不同类型的程序；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=18  style="margin-left:21.2500pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:-21.2500pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >4)<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(36,41,46);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);" ><font face="宋体" >对程序的编写语言无限制，可支持任何能够通过</font>Shell命令运行的语言，如Scala、Java、Python等；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><h3 style="mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >1.18.3<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >平台总体框架</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></b></h3><p class=18  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >项目主要由三大</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >部分</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >组成，包括</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >分布式的机器学习算法库，</font><a name="OLE_LINK3" ><font face="宋体" >基于</font>GUI的机器学习任务构建环境</a><font face="宋体" >系统，基于</font>Docker的云计算服务。&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=18  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >分布式的机器学习算法库不仅能实现流行的机器学习算法，也能实现数据预处理／后处理、数据格式转变、特征生成、表现评估等算法。</font>&nbsp;<font face="宋体" >同时，对于算法的编程语言无限制，可支持任何能够通过</font>Shell命令行运行的语言，如Scala，Java，Python等。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=18  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >基于</font>GUI的机器学习任务构建环境系统</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >，能让用户以拖曳的方式创建、配置、提交、监控、共享他们的机器学习流程。机器学习库中所有的算法都可在此开发环境系统中获得并使用，它们是构建机器学习任务的主要基础。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><i></i></span></p><p class=18  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >基于</font>Docker云计算服务使用Docker容器技术，搭建Hadoop集群，构建分布式管理和云计算服务。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >从</font>&nbsp;GUI&nbsp;上提交一个&nbsp;DAG&nbsp;任务之后，在所有的独立数据源准备好时，每个节点将会自动运行。对应节点的算法将会依据节点的具体实现而选择在&nbsp;Linux、Spark&nbsp;或者&nbsp;Map-Reduce上自动运行。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;